# Lab Branding, Test Pricing & Invoice Generator — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

Three additive features deployed without altering any existing functionality:

### Feature 1 — Lab Branding (Settings)
- Added **Lab Profile** section to [Settings.jsx](file:///h:/Webiste%20Projects/Lab%20Software/frontend/src/pages/Settings.jsx) (admin-only)
- Fields: Lab Name, Logo (image upload), Tagline, Address, Phone 1/2/3, Email, License Number
- Backend: `lab_settings` table + [lab-settings.js](file:///h:/Webiste%20Projects/Lab%20Software/backend/src/routes/lab-settings.js) route with multer file upload
- Logo served via `/uploads` static directory with vite proxy

### Feature 2 — Test Catalog Pricing
- Prices already display on the Test Catalog page (e.g. `PKR 200`, `PKR 1,500`)
- Price field already existed in the TestModal for create/edit — no changes needed

### Feature 3 — Invoice Generator

**Database:** `invoices` + `invoice_items` tables with auto-numbered `INV-YYYY-XXXX` sequence

**Auto-creation:** Invoice created atomically when a new sample order is placed — snapshots patient name, referring doctor, test names, and prices

**Invoice Preview in New Sample Modal:**
- Shows itemized tests with prices when tests are selected
- Discount amount + reason, Payment method, Amount paid fields
- Real-time calculated Net Payable, Balance Due, and colored status badge (Unpaid/Partial/Paid)

**Invoices Management Page (`/invoices`):**
- Searchable, filterable table with status tabs (All / Unpaid / Partial / Paid)
- Columns: Invoice #, Patient, Date, Tests, Net Payable, Paid, Balance, Status
- Click → detail modal with test items, payment summary, and payment update form
- Print Invoice link opens `/invoices/:id/print`

**Print Invoice Page:**
- A4 print-optimized layout with lab branding header
- Patient info, itemized test table, payment summary
- PAID watermark stamp when fully paid
- Auto-triggers `window.print()` on load

